          "notes": "Module has strong conceptual accuracy and up-to-date case studies (D2), but critically fails on narrative integrity and applied outcomes. The content is lecture-based with minimal story framing; lessons open with facts and cases rather than compelling problems learners must solve. Labs are conversational AI exchanges with no clear success criteria, measurable outputs, or scaffolded hands-on activities—learners cannot verify completion or demonstrate new capability.",
